content.rendered:
Directed by Venky Atluri

Written by Venky Atluri. P. Sathish Chandra

Cast Nithiin(Arjun). Keerthy Suresh(Anupama ‘Anu’). V.K. Naresh(Prakash , Arjun’s father). Kousalya(Arjun’s mother). Rohini(Shailaja, Anu’s mother).Rajitha. Vineeth(Arjun’s brother-in-law). Vennela Kishore(Adivi Shankar Shastri). Brahmaji(Travel Agent Sarvesh). Satyam Rajesh(Seenu). Abhinav Gomatam(Yanam). Suhas(Suhas). Gayathri Raghuram(Sharadha , Arjun’s sister). Rajveer Ankur Singh(Professor). Gundu Sudharshan(Librarian). Kaavya Nayar(Simran). Ronit Kamra(Chintu). Ram Charan Teja(Arjun at 10 years (as Charan Ram)). Hridaan(Young Arjun). Amaana(Young Anu). Drithi(Young Anu).Kadambari Kiran.Prabhu.Deepthi Varma.Akshitha Harish.Muskan Arora.Vaishnavi Chaitanya.Ananth.Indhu Anand.Anjaneyulu.Haasini.Vihaan.Azmath Khan.Fidaa.Chandramogli Madem

Language Telugu

Producers Suryadevara Naga Vamsi. S. Venkatarathnam.

Production Sithara Entertainments
